Pentoshi 🐧 euroPeng 🇪🇺: In 18' I was down 90% on my portfolio. And many of you are in the same spot. Of course it feels like the market will never come back when in that position. But it will, bc that's human nature. New whales will be made. Greed always returns. It's just often a 2 year wait in-between
